OL,3,CPandora to switch from silver to
OL,4,Cplatinum jewellery amid soaring prices
OL,6,FDanish jewellery brand Pandora will
OL,7,Fintroduce platinum-plated products to
OL,8,Freduce its reliance on silver, which
OL,9,Fis growing increasingly expensive.
OL,11,FThe prices of precious metals has
OL,12,Fcontinued to soar in the last year,
OL,13,Fwith silver more than doubling in
OL,14,Fvalue.
