OL,3,CPandora to switch from silver to
OL,4,Cplatinum jewellery amid soaring prices
OL,6,FAlthough platinum has also sharply
OL,7,Fincreased in price and is more
OL,8,Fexpensive than silver per ounce,
OL,9,FPandora plans to manufacture platinum-
OL,10,Fplated alloy-core jewellery, which
OL,11,Fwill be cheaper to produce than pure
OL,12,Fsilver pieces.
OL,14,FBerta de Pablos-Barbier, CEO of
OL,15,FPandora, said: "With this innovation,
OL,16,Fwe can navigate the new realities of
OL,17,Fraw material costs while offering
OL,18,Fconsumers precious metal jewellery
OL,19,Fthat is exceptionally well-suited for
OL,20,Feveryday wear."
