OL,3,CPandora to switch from silver to
OL,4,Cplatinum jewellery amid soaring prices
OL,6,FThe firm was founded in Copenhagen in
OL,7,F1982, and now has stores in more than
OL,8,F100 countries.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
