OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIn the first quarter of 2026, Pandora
OL,16,Fwill launch a selection platinum-
OL,17,Fplated versions of its best-selling
OL,18,Fbracelets across 30 stores in Northern
OL,19,FEurope. This will precede a global
OL,20,Flaunch in the second half of the year.
