OL,3,CPandora to switch from silver to
OL,4,Cplatinum jewellery amid soaring prices
OL,6,FThe platinum-plating process will be
OL,7,Finspired by the company's Evershine
OL,8,Fline of gold-plated products, launched
OL,9,Fin 2015.
OL,11,FAccording to the Financial Times,
OL,12,FPandora will move from making around
OL,13,F60 per cent of its jewellery from
OL,14,Fsilver to about 20 per cent by the end
OL,15,Fof 2028.
OL,17,F"It's highly frustrating when you are
OL,18,Fa highly desirable jewellery brand to
OL,19,Fbe considered a silver trading
OL,20,Fcompany," de Pablos-Barbier told the
OL,21,FFinancial Times.
